00:00:12.625 --> 00:00:13.660
- The power of the social brain

00:00:13.660 --> 00:00:15.940
has been totally underestimated.

00:00:15.940 --> 00:00:17.930
It's a driving force in learning.

00:00:17.930 --> 00:00:20.070
It's the gateway to cognition.

00:00:20.070 --> 00:00:22.680
We have evidence that the social brain

00:00:22.680 --> 00:00:26.150
is operating to assist learning
throughout the lifespan.

00:00:26.150 --> 00:00:28.300
So let's think about human babies.

00:00:28.300 --> 00:00:30.560
We know in the development of language

00:00:30.560 --> 00:00:32.410
that there's a very important period

00:00:32.410 --> 00:00:34.940
between six months and 12 months of age

00:00:34.940 --> 00:00:37.690
where babies are mastering
the sounds of language.

00:00:37.690 --> 00:00:40.730
So we've done experiments
in which babies are exposed

00:00:40.730 --> 00:00:43.283
to a foreign language right
at that critical moment.

00:00:43.283 --> 00:00:46.330
(speaking in Mandarin)

00:00:46.330 --> 00:00:48.010
- They're listening to a Mandarin speaker

00:00:48.010 --> 00:00:50.370
when they're growing up
in an English family.

00:00:50.370 --> 00:00:53.550
What we've demonstrated is
that if a baby at nine months

00:00:53.550 --> 00:00:57.760
has 12 sessions of play
with a live human speaker,

00:00:57.760 --> 00:01:00.960
they learn so well that they're
statistically equivalent

00:01:00.960 --> 00:01:02.540
to the babies in the foreign country

00:01:02.540 --> 00:01:04.740
who've been listening for 10 months;

00:01:04.740 --> 00:01:07.960
however, if the babies are
exposed to the same material

00:01:07.960 --> 00:01:10.240
at the same time, same room, same dosage,

00:01:10.240 --> 00:01:12.800
but not exposed to a live human being

00:01:12.800 --> 00:01:16.940
and instead on a beautiful
DVD, they stare at it,

00:01:16.940 --> 00:01:18.670
you think they're learning,

00:01:18.670 --> 00:01:20.770
but the brain tests following exposure

00:01:20.770 --> 00:01:24.580
show that the kids in the
machine group learned nothing.

00:01:24.580 --> 00:01:27.690
The babies in the live
group learned so well

00:01:27.690 --> 00:01:29.970
they matched the babies
in the foreign country.

00:01:29.970 --> 00:01:31.800
- Eli, when there was...

00:01:31.800 --> 00:01:32.633
